					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Setting PPUSCROLL ($2005) and PPUCTRL ($2000) is enough, but you need to do it <em>after</em> drawing, at the <em>end</em> of your vblank code, just before you turn rendering back on in PPUMASK ($2001). Don't do it in your NMI handler unless your NMI handler is handling all the drawing.</div>

